<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="en"><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.4.1">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://chongfengling.github.io/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml"/><link href="https://chongfengling.github.io/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" hreflang="en"/><updated>2026-03-13T05:15:25+00:00</updated><id>https://chongfengling.github.io/feed.xml</id><title type="html">blank</title><subtitle>A simple, whitespace theme for academics. Based on [*folio](https://github.com/bogoli/-folio) design. </subtitle><entry><title type="html">学术博文案例：数学与代码</title><link href="https://chongfengling.github.io/blog/2024/academic-post-template/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="学术博文案例：数学与代码"/><published>2024-05-20T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2024-05-20T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://chongfengling.github.io/blog/2024/academic-post-template</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://chongfengling.github.io/blog/2024/academic-post-template/"><![CDATA[<p>这是一篇示例文章，展示了学术写作中常用的排版功能。</p> <h3 id="1-数学公式展示">1. 数学公式展示</h3> <p>你可以使用 LaTeX 语法插入行内公式，例如：$E = mc^2$。</p> <p>也可以插入块级公式：</p> \[\int_{a}^{b} f(x) dx = F(b) - F(a)\] <h3 id="2-代码片段展示">2. 代码片段展示</h3> <p>这是一个 Python 代码块示例：</p> <div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">fibonacci</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">a</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">b</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">_</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nf">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="k">yield</span> <span class="n">a</span>
        <span class="n">a</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">b</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">b</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">a</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">b</span>
</code></pre></div></div> <p>保存后运行 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">bundle exec jekyll serve</code> 即可在本地看到效果。</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="tutorial"/><category term="academic"/><category term="formatting"/><category term="math"/><category term="code"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[这是一篇展示如何在 al-folio 中使用数学公式和代码高亮的案例文章。]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Displaying External Posts on Your al-folio Blog</title><link href="https://chongfengling.github.io/blog/2022/displaying-external-posts-on-your-al-folio-blog/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Displaying External Posts on Your al-folio Blog"/><published>2022-04-23T23:20:09+00:00</published><updated>2022-04-23T23:20:09+00:00</updated><id>https://chongfengling.github.io/blog/2022/displaying-external-posts-on-your-al-folio-blog</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://chongfengling.github.io/blog/2022/displaying-external-posts-on-your-al-folio-blog/"><![CDATA[]]></content><author><name></name></author></entry></feed>